</div>
			<h1 id="firstHeading" class="firstHeading" lang="en">International Sahaja Public School</h1>
									<div id="bodyContent" class="mw-body-content">
									<div id="siteSub">From Wikipedia, the free encyclopedia</div>
								<div id="contentSub"></div>
												<div id="jump-to-nav" class="mw-jump">
					Jump to:					<a href="#mw-head">navigation</a>, 					<a href="#p-search">search</a>
				</div>
				<div id="mw-content-text" lang="en" dir="ltr" class="mw-content-ltr"><p>The <b>International Sahaja Public School</b> in <a href="/wiki/Dharamsala,_Himachal_Pradesh" title="Dharamsala, Himachal Pradesh" class="mw-redirect">Dharamsala</a>, <a href="/wiki/India" title="India">India</a> is a school run by the <a href="/wiki/Sahaja_Yoga" title="Sahaja Yoga">Sahaja Yoga</a> movement. The school was founded in 1990.</p>
<p></p>
<div id="toc" class="toc">
<div id="toctitle">
<h2>Contents</h2>
</div>
<ul>
<li class="toclevel-1 tocsection-1"><a href="#Overview"><span class="tocnumber">1</span> <span class="toctext">Overview</span></a></li>
